BEGIN:VEVENT
CREATED:20260629T134035Z
DESCRIPTION:Location: Room 7304 - Convocation Center\n\nOur focus on day 
 1 will be introducing you to the history and mission of the school and b
 eginning our on-going professional discussion about classroom management
 .  For those of you in the classroom\, please come having read the two c
 hapters from The Skillful Teacher (pdf attached)\, and think about what 
 classroom norms\, policies\, and routines you’d like to establish.*   Pl
 ease have a first draft of your course policy sheet ready for each cours
 e.  You can access a course policy template here\, but you should also f
 eel free to borrow and adapt a course policy sheet from a colleague or d
 evelop your own.  
