DTEND:20260616T130000Z
DTSTAMP:20260716T170359Z
UID:AE021662-8E0B-4F8C-983E-AEF30625ACA8
CREATED:20260616T112852Z
DESCRIPTION:How to get there: Yoga Sangha is located one the second floor o
 f 2032 P Street Northwest\, Washington\, DC 20036 above Emissary.\n\nAmenit
 ies: Mats\n\nHow to prepare: Wear comfortable clothing you can move easily 
 in. Bring a mat if you have one and water if you'd like.\n\nWhen to arrive:
  15 minutes before\n\nAbout this class: Start the day on your own terms. Th
 is morning flow wakes the body gently and clears the mind before the world 
 asks anything of you. Move with your breath\, build a little heat\, and set
  a steadier rhythm for the hours ahead. Step off the mat clear\, open and r
 eady for your day.\n\nAbout this studio: Yoga Sangha is more than just a pl
 ace to practice\; it's a vibrant community where wellness and togetherness 
 are at the heart of everything we do. We believe in creating a warm\, invit
 ing space where everyone feels welcome\, regardless of experience level. Ou
 r dedicated instructors are not only skilled in various yoga styles but are
  also passionate about fostering connections and supporting each student's 
 journey.\n\nWe offer a range of classes designed to promote physical\, ment
 al\, and emotional well-being. From calming\, restorative sessions to energ
 izing vinyasa flows\, there's something for everyone. Our studio also hosts
  regular workshops\, social events\, and community outreach programs\, rein
 forcing our commitment to holistic wellness and the strength of community.\
 n\nJoin us to experience the transformative power of yoga in a supportive\,
  nurturing environment. Here\, you'll find not just a place to practice\, b
 ut a place to belong. \n\n\n\nContact number: 2028383131\n\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20260616T112853Z
LOCATION:2032 P Street Northwest  Washington
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Morning Vinyasa
TRANSP:OPAQUE
