 p dive into the world of emotion</blockquote><br><br><i>Sam will discuss wh
 y we react the way we do. She'll trace the roots of our communication style
 s from childhood to adulthood\, look at the Enneagram as a developmental ma
 p\, and share a few anonymized stories from her coaching work to show how E
 Q plays out in real life. </i>\n\nJoin with Google Meet: https://meet.googl
 e.com/ges-zwgw-fpe\nOr dial: (US) +1 260-297-0088 PIN: 399652621#\nMore pho
 ne numbers: https://tel.meet/ges-zwgw-fpe?pin=1851499528548&hs=7\n\nLearn m
 ore about Meet at: https://support.google.com/a/users/answer/9282720
LAST-MODIFIED:20260708T024341Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Passion Project Presentation #2  
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT

