CREATED:20260511T144806Z
DESCRIPTION:Event Name\nGuidewell Education Recruiter Chat\n\nHi! Andrew he
 re\, In-house Recruiter at Guidewell Education. We really enjoyed your vide
 o interview and are excited to keep the conversation moving.\n\nThe Goal: T
 his call is a chance for me to ask a few follow-up questions regarding your
  candidacy and for us to dive into your experience as well as discuss logis
 tics.\n\nThe Format: Please feel free to choose either a phone or video cal
 l. I’m always happy to meet face-to-face\, but I totally understand if a ph
 one call is easier for your schedule.\n\nA Quick Note: We use Google Gemini
  to record a transcript of interviews. This helps me stay present in the co
 nversation rather than focused on taking notes in real time. It's strictly 
 for summarizing our discussion and isn't used to make hiring decisions.\n\n
 Location: This is a Google Meet web conference.\nYou can join this meeting 
 from your computer\, tablet\, or smartphone.\nhttps://calendly.com/events/9
 7b56b29-546b-45b8-bd58-40fcdbace7ec/google_meet\n\nNeed to make changes to 
 this event?\nCancel: https://calendly.com/cancellations/54b0f9b7-8038-48db-
 9dbc-bb7ab272db88\nReschedule: https://calendly.com/reschedulings/54b0f9b7-
 8038-48db-9dbc-bb7ab272db88\n\n\nJoin with Google Meet: https://meet.google
 .com/fht-qvke-wbf\nOr dial: (US) +1 319-346-6130 PIN: 690304798#\nMore phon
 e numbers: https://tel.meet/fht-qvke-wbf?pin=4343158998223&hs=7\n\nLearn mo
 re about Meet at: https://support.google.com/a/users/answer/9282720
LAST-MODIFIED:20260513T180044Z
LOCATION:Google Meet (instructions in description)
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Cosette Rhoads and Andrew Clark-Spring
