 D: 834 3795 2189\nPasscode: 374300\n\n\nThe Office of Development and Alumn
 i Relations invites you to an exclusive campus connection webinar focused o
 n summer internships and spring break externships with Kelly Harris\, assis
 tant dean & director of employer engagement\, Donna Miller\, assistant dean
  & executive director of career communities\, and Robin Bourjaily\, assista
 nt director\, exploratory career community in the Center for Careers\, Life
 \, and Service (CLS).\n\nDuring our time together\, they will give an updat
 e on the College's internships and externships processes. Come learn more a
 bout how our students connect knowledge gained in the classroom and in thes
 e experiential programs to plan for their future endeavors.\n\n
