DESCRIPTION:Epic Yoga DC\n\nInstructor: Melanie Smith\n\nDescription\n=====
 ======\n45 minute class combining elements of yoga sculpt and barre. Class 
 will begin with simple stretches that transition into movements designed to
  build heat\, strengthen the core\, and enhance mobility. Areas of emphasis
  include sun salutations\, sculpting of arms and legs\, abdominal focus\, a
 nd balance work. Class may be done with bodyweight or include equipment suc
 h as light weights\, resistance bands\, and sliders.
