BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:UPCOMING_PLAN_WORKOUT-72c2500f-9425-4e1d-b53a-993c2810f334_plan_week_3_HILLS_0
DTSTAMP:20260715
DTSTART:20260717
DTEND:20260718
SUMMARY:🏃 Alternating Hill Reps • 2.5mi
DESCRIPTION:Hills • 2.5mi • 25m - 30m\n\n1mi warm up at a conversational pace (no faster than 11:15/mi), while jogging to base of hill\n\n2 reps of:\n• 60s running hard uphill, 30s walking rest. Easy jog back down.\n• 30s running hard uphill, 20s walking rest. Easy jog back down.\n\n0.75mi cool down at a conversational pace (or slower!)\n\n📲 View in the Runna app: https://club.runna.com/n9Tx/workout?dayId=72c2500f-9425-4e1d-b53a-993c2810f334_plan_week_3_HILLS_0&weekIndex=3
X-USER-TIMEZONE:America/New_York
X-WORKOUT-ESTIMATED-DURATION:1800
X-SHOULD-UPDATE:true
END:VEVENT


