SUMMARY:🏃 3.75mi Progressive Long Run
DESCRIPTION:📊 Summary:\nDistance: 3.75mi\nTime: 48:50\nAvg Pace: 13:00 /mi\n\n📋 Description:\nWas looking forward to this run! I definitely needed the warm up to loosen up and warm up my lungs, even after lifting. I hadnt checked the pace that Runna recomended for the second rep before I started the workout, and I was shocked when it was only an increase of 0.1 mph, then only another 0.2 to get to RPE 6. It felt good, definitely took effort but was manageable, feeling strong!\n——\n1.5mi at a conversational pace\n1.25mi at RPE 5\n1mi at RPE 6\n\n♻️ Laps:\n1.50 mi @ 13:16 /mi\n1.25 mi @ 13:02 /mi\n1.00 mi @ 12:24 /mi\n0.00 mi @ 1:02:49 /mi\n📲 View in the Runna app: https://club.runna.com/n9Tx/activities?activityId=e3b8648e-5ac1-4b69-89b1-259ac2aa9aab
