DTSTAMP:20260106T150300
DTSTART:20260105T173000
DTEND:20260105T183000
SUMMARY:Monday Afternoon Strength
DESCRIPTION:📋 Description:\nLift felt so good! Kept the weight super low, basically just bodyweight, and I still feel a little tight and sore post-break…\n\n——\n10 min warmup\n\nMain set:\n1. Superset 3x\n    * Barbell back backwards lunge, 8 reps each side, training bar only\n    * Barbell back squat, 10-12 reps, training bar only\n2. SLRDL, 3x8 each side, 15 lb kb\n3. Single arm row, 3x8 each side, 15 lb kb\n4. Chest press, 3x8, training bar\n\n5 mins abs\n5 mins stretching/cooldown\n\n\n\n📲 View in the Runna app: https://club.runna.com/n9Tx/activities?activityId=8e5fb2a0-8180-4528-9ccc-b0dde28e3d47
X-USER-TIMEZONE:America/New_York
END:VEVENT


