DTSTAMP:20260107T023424
DTSTART:20260106T173000
DTEND:20260106T183000
SUMMARY:Tuesday Afternoon Strength
DESCRIPTION:📋 Description:\nI felt so sore today even after my light day yesterday 😭 kept the lifts light today as well, I was very happy that I stretched out before/after, feels like my muscles are waking back up ☀️\n\n——\n10 min warmup\n\nMain set:\n1. Superset 3x\n    * Calf raises, 10-12 reps, 2x15 lb kbs\n    * Tibialis raises, 8-10 reps each side, 15 lb kb\n2. Hip thrust, 3x8, training bar onlh\n3. Superset 3x\n    * Seated shoulder press, 10 reps, 2x15 lbs\n    * Bicep curl, 8 reps, 2x8 lbs\n4. Pull-up variations (lat activation, hangs)\n\n5 mins abs\n5 mins stretching/cooldown\n\n📲 View in the Runna app: https://club.runna.com/n9Tx/activities?activityId=93c3a75d-2a65-47ef-b831-3b721bb2d0a3
X-USER-TIMEZONE:America/New_York
END:VEVENT


